word: G368 - ἀναντίῤῥητος - anantírrhētos - an-an-tir'-hray-tos - Cannot be spoken against

sections.paragraph: சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: Cannot be spoken against
not contradicted and not to be contradicted; undeniable
ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: From G1 (as a negatively particle) and a presumed derivative of a compound of G473 and G4483; indisputable: - cannot be spoken against.
